        "LIMERICK": "A nonsense poem of five anapestic lines, of which  lines 1, 2,and 5 are of there feet, and rime, and lines 3 and 4 are of two feet,and rime; as --",
        "LIMESTONE": "A rock consisting chiefly of calcium carbonate or carbonate oflime. It sometimes contains also magnesium carbonate, and is thencalled magnesian or dolomitic limestone. Crystalline limestone iscalled marble.",
