        "LOMBARDIC": "Of or pertaining to Lombardy of the Lombards. Lombardicalphabet, the ancient alphabet derived from the Roman, and employedin the manuscript of Italy.-- Lombardic architecture, the debased Roman style of architectureas found in parts of Northern Italy. F. G. Lee. Lombardy poplar.(Bot.) See Poplar.",
