        "LUCKLESS": "Being without luck; unpropitious; unfortunate; unlucky; meetingwith ill success or bad fortune; as, a luckless gamester; a lucklessmaid.Prayers made and granted in a luckless hour. Dryden.-- Luck\"less*ly, adv.-- Lock\"less*ness, n.",
